extends ./wrapper.jade

block content
    h2 Request for Course Consideration
    br
    p
      | If the course you are looking to transfer does not show up in the course selection page, you can create a request for review here. Fill out all fields to assist the Admissions department with identifying your course:
    br
    form(action='/admission/transfer/credits/app/requestCourseConfirmation',method='POST')
      | Course Name: 
      input(type='text', name='courseName')
      br
      | Course Number: 
      input(type='text', name='courseNumber')
      br
      | Course Description: 
      textarea(name='courseDescription')
      br
      | School:
      select(id='schools',name='schools')
            each school in schools
                option(value=school, selected=selected)= school
      br
      input(type='submit',value='Select School')
